+# Setup Guide
+
+## Prerequisites
+
+- Docker 24+
+- Node.js 20+
+- Python 3.12+
+
+## Environment Variables
+
+Copy `.env.example` to `.env` and fill in the values:
+
+- `DATABASE_URL` — PostgreSQL connection string
+- `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` — API key for Claude models
